Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜很喜欢这个旋律呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是自己编的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没画完呢 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊来啊 过来拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷欧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:01:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多克老师吗 他还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又胖了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就像熊先生一样 很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软啪啪的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是肥嘟嘟的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来比起守卫 他更适合当老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 我不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命 谁来救救我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷欧 雷欧 雷欧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多克老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.11,0:03:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷欧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:03:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跳下来 我会接住的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜 快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜讨厌我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不相信我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拿出勇气来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很努力哦 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到你了 雷欧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里也许还有其他人需要帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜不想见小义和小纱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我没回来就去八丁镇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那里后向官府求助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就…那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是久违的任务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是什么值得兴奋的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与火之国接壤的边境小国的小村庄发生了惨案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说那里的居民惨遭灭门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亘古以来 那里就被视为圣域
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人称巨坑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传言那里藏有秘宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打击觊觎秘宝的盗贼们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里防守严密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全军覆没也太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽想尽可能增派人手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但村里如今也不太平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前日发生的村外临时墓地被破坏事件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且封印着晓成员的森林里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前那起镰刀被盗事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我们要忙上一阵子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不能无视平民们的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挖出袭击村子的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给予其应得的制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上都烧成灰烬了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙是用什么武器袭击村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好壮观的树林啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面明明是寸草不生的荒野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里应该是宝库吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的泉水应该通往某处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下竟有如此的空间…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可思议的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被盗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想趁火打劫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是受命而来的木叶忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前来调查这座村子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此事有所耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是守护附近八丁镇的警卫队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和托尼卡村交好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人向你引见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些贵客是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你们如此迅速前来支援
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫迪索纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是八丁镇的镇长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前日那些幸免于难的村民们前来求助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以得知了此事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有任何入侵者的线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村子的守卫和觊觎秘宝的盗贼们有过多次冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道那个宝物到底是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕村里了解真相的也不多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:16:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说根本不知道是谁为了什么而袭击这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的水真甜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真的很美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这巨坑简直就像在吸收周围的活力和生息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讴歌着繁荣一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的泉水充满着生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二位 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是那么爱打架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这附近想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在做一些研究
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些蛇是我用大蛇丸大人的细胞制成的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏其强大的再生力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弹指间便能大量繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 借助我伟大的实验成果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以移植其他生物的细胞核
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重现遗传信息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧合的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的水能够迅速促进细胞分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和病毒不相上下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后 重生…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是晓的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是 飞段
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你出现在这里不是偶然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击村子的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好给我解释解释 说说经过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓得到…我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不会让你逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棋子并非就此一枚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是…晓的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯玛老师和疾风老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…秽土转生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你盗的墓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来会很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道忍术的火候还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 千万别被对方碰到血液
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.04,0:22:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 快无法呼吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上古之神创造的天之矛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被污秽之人夺去了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那股足以颠覆世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要将世界毁于一旦
